# PhonePe Transaction Data Analysis Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project analyzes PhonePe transaction data using Power BI to identify digital payment trends across India.

## Objectives
- Analyze state-wise transaction data
- Identify growth patterns in digital payments
- Visualize user engagement trends

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel

## Key Insights
- State-wise transaction distribution
- Digital payment growth trends
- User engagement patterns

## Dashboard
Interactive Power BI dashboard created to visualize transaction trends and insights.

